  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some cool Pok\u00e9mon GO gadgets to buy?",
  "response": "There are several gadgets that can enhance your Pok\u00e9mon GO experience. Here are some popular ones:\n\n1. **Pok\u00e9mon GO Plus**: This wearable device connects to your smartphone via Bluetooth and allows you to catch Pok\u00e9mon and collect items from Pok\u00e9Stops without having to look at your phone. It vibrates and lights up to notify you of nearby Pok\u00e9mon or Pok\u00e9Stops.\n\n2. **Pok\u00e9 Ball Plus**: Similar to the Pok\u00e9mon GO Plus, this device can also be used with the Nintendo Switch games Pok\u00e9mon: Let's Go, Pikachu! and Let's Go, Eevee! It allows you to catch Pok\u00e9mon and collect items in Pok\u00e9mon GO and can be used as a Joy-Con controller for the Switch games.\n\n3. **Go-tcha**: This is an unofficial alternative to the Pok\u00e9mon GO Plus that offers additional features such as auto-catching Pok\u00e9mon and auto-spinning Pok\u00e9Stops. It has a sleek design and is often favored by players for its convenience.\n\n4. **Power Banks**: Pok\u00e9mon GO is a battery-intensive game, so having a reliable power bank can be a lifesaver during long play sessions. Look for power banks with high capacity (10,000 mAh or more) to ensure you can keep playing without interruption.\n\n5. **Phone Mounts and Holders**: If you play Pok\u00e9mon GO while biking or driving (safely, of course), a phone mount can help keep your hands free and your phone secure. Look for mounts that are sturdy and easy to adjust.\n\n6. **Portable Chargers and Charging Cables**: Extra charging cables and portable chargers are always handy to have, especially if you plan on playing for extended periods or during community events.\n\n7. **Screen Protectors and Phone Cases**: Protect your phone from drops and scratches with a good-quality screen protector and a rugged phone case. This is especially important if you're playing outdoors frequently.\n\n8. **Fitness Bands**: Since Pok\u00e9mon GO encourages walking and physical activity, a fitness band or smartwatch can help you track your steps, distance, and other health metrics. Some fitness bands can also sync with your phone to notify you of in-game events.\n\nThese gadgets can help make your Pok\u00e9mon GO experience more enjoyable and efficient.",
